#: Naia/macros/weapon-specials.cfg:40 Naia/macros/weapon-specials.cfg:41
msgid "attack only"
msgstr "Solo ataque"

#. [damage]: id=attack_only
#: Naia/macros/weapon-specials.cfg:42 Naia/macros/weapon-specials.cfg:43
msgid "This weapon will never be used on defense."
